import { Button, ButtonGroup, Flex, Spacer, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import React from "react";


 const Header=()=>{
    return(
    <Flex>
        <Text>My TMDB</Text>
        <Spacer/>
        <ButtonGroup>
        <Button>Movies</Button>
        <Button>TV</Button>
        </ButtonGroup>
        <Spacer/>
        <ButtonGroup>
        <Button>Log In</Button>
        <Button>Register</Button>
        </ButtonGroup>
    </Flex>)
    
}


export default Header
